<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/fr.26.e93456.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Basal neornithischian specimens from the lower Phu Kradung Formation. (left) Left dentary (PRC 149) from Phu Noi locality, in lateral (A) and medial (B) views; (right) isolated tooth (WNM-Ks- 001) from Khok Sanam locality, in labial (if dentary) (C), lingual (D) and mesial / distal (E) views. Scale bars: 5 cm (A, B); 1 cm (C-E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/793762" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

